
    <html>
    
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <title>Adventure Park Challenge</title>
    
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    
        <style>
            body {
                background-color: #102018;
                color: #f0f0f0;
                font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                text-align: center;
                padding: 30px;
            }
    
            h1 {
                color: #ffcc33;
            }
    
            h2 {
                color: #ffffff;
                margin-top: 30px;
            }
    
            h3 {
                color: #ffffff;
            }
    
            small {
                color: #bbbbbb;
            }
    
            dl {
                text-align: left;
                display: inline-block;
            }
    
            dt {
                color: #ffcc33;
                font-weight: bold;
            }
    
            dd {
                color: #dddddd;
            }
    
            mark {
                background-color: #ffcc33;
                color: #000000;
                padding: 2px 6px;
                border-radius: 4px;
            }
    
            code {
                background-color: #07130d;
                color: #66ff99;
                padding: 2px 8px;
                border-radius: 4px;
                font-size: 16px;
            }
    
            abbr {
                color: #ffcc33;
                font-weight: bold;
                cursor: help;
            }
    
            pre {
                background-color: #07130d;
                color: #66ff99;
                padding: 15px;
                border-radius: 8px;
                display: inline-block;
                text-align: left;
            }
    
            blockquote {
                border-left: 4px solid #ffcc33;
                padding-left: 15px;
                color: #cccccc;
                font-style: italic;
                display: inline-block;
                text-align: left;
            }
    
            hr {
                border-color: #2f4f3f;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    
    <body>
    
        <h1>Welcome to Adventure Park Challenge!</h1>
        <p>Get ready to explore rides, challenges, and safety missions while learning typography in HTML and Bootstrap.</p>
    
        <hr>
    
        <h2>Adventure Levels</h2>
        <p class="display-1">Extreme Explorer</p>
        <p class="display-2">Mountain Rider</p>
        <p class="display-3">Trail Runner</p>
        <p class="display-4">New Adventurer</p>
    
        <hr>
    
        <h2>Visitor Passes</h2>
        <h3>Aarav <small>Pass: Extreme Explorer</small></h3>
        <h3>Mia <small>Pass: Mountain Rider</small></h3>
        <h3>Zara <small>Pass: Trail Runner</small></h3>
    
        <hr>
    
        <h2>Ride Dictionary</h2>
        <dl>
            <dt>Sky Coaster</dt>
            <dd>A fast ride that takes visitors high above the park.</dd>
    
            <dt>Treasure Trail</dt>
            <dd>A mystery path where visitors solve clues to find treasure.</dd>
    
            <dt>River Rush</dt>
            <dd>A water ride that moves quickly through twists and turns.</dd>
        </dl>
    
        <hr>
    
        <h2>Safety Mission</h2>
        <p>Please report to <mark>Gate 3</mark> before the challenge begins.</p>
        <p>The rescue drill will happen near <mark>River Zone</mark>.</p>
    
        <hr>
    
        <h2>Ride Commands</h2>
        <p>Start the coaster: <code>ride.start("Sky Coaster")</code></p>
        <p>Open the trail: <code>trail.open("Treasure Trail")</code></p>
        <p>Stop the ride: <code>ride.stop("River Rush")</code></p>
    
        <hr>
    
        <h2>Park Short Forms</h2>
        <p><abbr title="Adventure Park Safety Team">APST</abbr> checks every ride before opening.</p>
        <p><abbr title="River Rescue Unit">RRU</abbr> helps visitors near water rides.</p>
        <p><abbr title="Junior Explorer Club">JEC</abbr> is for young adventure lovers.</p>
    
        <hr>
    
    
        <h2>Daily Challenge Schedule</h2>
        <pre>
    10:00 AM  -  Gate Entry
    11:00 AM  -  Sky Coaster
    12:00 PM  -  Treasure Trail
    02:00 PM  -  River Rush
    03:00 PM  -  Final Adventure Badge
      </pre>
    
        <hr>
    
        <h2>Adventure Quote</h2>
        <blockquote class="blockquote">
            <p>"Adventure begins when you try something new."</p>
            <footer class="blockquote-footer">Adventure Park Team</footer>
        </blockquote>
    
    </body>
    
    </html>